│   Intake    │ ← Initial classification
└─────┬───────┘
      ↓
┌─────────────┐
│  Research   │ ← RAG retrieval
└─────┬───────┘
      ↓
┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐
│  Can Answer │──No→│  Escalate   │
└─────┬───────┘     └─────────────┘
      ↓ Yes
┌─────────────┐
│  Respond    │
└─────┬───────┘
      ↓
┌─────────────┐
│  Confirm    │ ← User satisfied?
└─────────────┘
```

**Why it works:**
- Predictable behavior
- Easier testing per state
- Clear escalation points
- Cost control via state limits

