- vLLM Team. "PagedAttention: Software-Defined Memory for LLM Serving" (2024/2025)
- NVIDIA. "Optimizing Inference with TensorRT-LLM" (2025)
- Anthropic. "Prompt Caching: Scale while reducing costs" (2024/2025)

